    "body": "You can check the search paths of Node modules in `module.paths`, if your `resources/js` is not in it, then `require` won't be able to find `test.js`.\n\nI think it is because you didn't manipulate the module search paths correctly, you might be a bee to get some ideas in [the community](https://github.com/atom/electron#community).\n"
